24:30.535 --> 24:32.803
Ain't you had enough
of that shit?

24:41.213 --> 24:42.680
Dad.

24:44.850 --> 24:46.650
Put the bottle down.

24:47.586 --> 24:49.019
What the fuck?

24:59.030 --> 25:01.799
-Dad!
-[PANTING]

25:04.102 --> 25:05.536
No!

25:05.971 --> 25:08.138
[GASPING]

25:11.142 --> 25:12.543
Dad!

25:12.545 --> 25:14.945
No, Dad! No!

25:16.882 --> 25:19.517
[PANTING]

25:21.253 --> 25:24.889
[STATIC BUZZING]

25:26.691 --> 25:27.925
[SIGHS]

25:34.165 --> 25:35.900
[SIGHS]

25:45.610 --> 25:48.612
JENNA: <i>I don't know</i>
<i>about your little angels...</i>

25:48.780 --> 25:50.981
[SHOWER RUNNING]

25:52.751 --> 25:54.018
Carly?

25:54.920 --> 25:56.220
JENNA:
...but mine steals from me

25:56.222 --> 25:58.022
<i>every chance she gets.</i>

26:04.629 --> 26:06.263
[SIGHS]

26:07.832 --> 26:09.833
