that's sort of
why I'm here today.

26:38.230 --> 26:43.901
Remember how you said
if ever I want to get back in...

26:44.369 --> 26:45.936
[LAUGHS]

26:45.938 --> 26:48.105
Oh, Kendall, that was, what,
