27:50.835 --> 27:52.036
Yep.

27:57.175 --> 27:59.977
-[SIREN WAILING]
-[TIRES SCREECH]

28:00.812 --> 28:02.379
God damn it!

28:03.281 --> 28:05.149
[SOBBING]

28:13.425 --> 28:14.458
RILEY: Yeah,
