29:33.172 --> 29:34.238
-What the fuck?
<i>-Multiple incidents</i>

29:34.240 --> 29:37.341
are being reported
of parents attacking...

29:37.343 --> 29:42.279
and, in many cases,
murdering their own children.

29:42.281 --> 29:43.547
Riley!

29:50.188 --> 29:51.522
RILEY: Mom?

29:51.524 --> 29:53.257
Are you okay?

29:55.560 --> 29:57.327
I spilled my drink.

