livestock will tell you--

30:08.374 --> 30:10.207
ANCHOR: Excuse me.
You are talking about pigs?

30:10.209 --> 30:13.210
There are children dying,
and you're talking about pigs.

30:13.212 --> 30:14.478
Well, yes. In fact,
around 50 percent

30:14.480 --> 30:17.981
of the piglet fatalities seen
is due to the mother attacking

30:17.983 --> 30:20.350
or crushing
the newborn pre-weaned babies,

30:20.352 --> 30:22.519
and no one can say
exactly why they do it.

30:22.521 --> 30:23.120
[RILEY GROANS]

30:23.122 --> 30:25.889
ANCHOR: [ON TV] <i>Again, we have</i>
<i>to emphasize, we have no idea</i>

30:25.891 --> 30:27.958
what set off the incidents,
<i>and authorities</i>

30:27.960 --> 30:31.328
<i>have so far refused</i>
<i>to issue any statement.</i>

30:31.330 --> 30:33.864
All we know is what we are...

30:33.898 --> 30:35.032
Riley?

30:35.034 --> 30:37.234
[JAZZ MUSIC PLAYING]

30:40.138 --> 30:41.038
Riley, I swear to God,

30:41.040 --> 30:44.508
if you're messing with me,
I'll kill you.

31:00.592 --> 31:03.060
-Hey, kiddo.
-[CARLY SCREAMS]

31:03.062 --> 31:05.596
NURSE: [ON PA] <i>Dr. Torres,</i>
<i>please dial...</i>

31:08.399 --> 31:10.067
ANCHOR: [ON TV] <i>All right,</i>
<i>but isn't it a fact</i>

31:10.069 --> 31:12.502
