<i>what is causing this?</i>

31:12.504 --> 31:13.937
MAN: [ON TV] <i>It could be</i>
<i>a natural phenomenon,</i>

31:13.939 --> 31:18.242
<i>but let's just postulate</i>
<i>someone wants to wipe us out,</i>

31:18.244 --> 31:19.610
<i>so they create</i>
<i>a biological weapon</i>

31:19.612 --> 31:25.182
