in front of a speeding car,

31:29.188 --> 31:31.488
<i>or an oncoming train</i>
<i>or even a wild animal</i>

31:31.490 --> 31:33.991
<i>to save their child,</i>
<i>but if you could take</i>

31:33.993 --> 31:37.094
that natural human impulse
<i>and reverse it,</i>

31:37.096 --> 31:38.495
