50:31.629 --> 50:34.397
in the middle of a crisis,
<i>is to protect them,</i>

50:34.399 --> 50:37.533
<i>but do not go</i>
<i>near your children.</i>

50:37.535 --> 50:39.268
[STATIC BUZZING]

50:42.773 --> 50:44.306
[SIGHS]

51:31.721 --> 51:33.389
Are you all right?

51:35.325 --> 51:36.592
[GROANS]

51:36.660 --> 51:38.294
Took a header.

51:39.796 --> 51:41.630
Must have blacked out.

51:43.100 --> 51:44.733
You're home early.

51:45.469 --> 51:46.869
So are you.

51:54.444 --> 51:56.345
They're in the basement.

52:01.184 --> 52:02.551
KENDALL: Carly?

52:02.752 --> 52:04.253
<i>Joshua?</i>

52:04.521 --> 52:06.422
<i>-Can you hear me?</i>
<i>-Mom?</i>

52:06.424 --> 52:07.423
Dude, shh.

52:07.425 --> 52:10.826
<i>Yes, it's Mommy.</i>
<i>Mommy's here.</i>

52:11.328 --> 52:13.195
<i>Is your sister with you?</i>

52:13.263 --> 52:16.499
-Yeah, Mom, I'm here.
-Oh, thank God.

52:16.666 --> 52:18.200
Are you two all right?

52:18.202 --> 52:20.302
[SOBBING]

52:20.570 --> 52:21.804
Mom...

52:21.905 --> 52:23.639
I stole the money...

52:24.174 --> 52:25.541
from your purse.

52:26.610 --> 52:27.510
I'm so sorry. I--

52:27.512 --> 52:29.745
Riley, she just said
that she needed it,

52:29.747 --> 52:31.547
and then her... [SOBBING]

52:32.516 --> 52:33.716
her mom...

52:33.718 --> 52:34.550
It's okay, honey.

52:34.552 --> 52:38.254
I understand. You must have had
a very good reason...

52:38.256 --> 52:40.689
but that's not what this
is about.

52:40.790 --> 52:42.291
Now I want you to unbolt
the door,

52:42.293 --> 52:45.928
and I want you and your brother
to come out of that basement.

52:45.930 --> 52:47.630
<i>Do you understand?</i>

52:47.864 --> 52:51.534
No, Mom, we're not coming out,
okay? You have to leave.

52:51.536 --> 52:52.168
[STATIC BUZZING]

52:52.170 --> 52:54.436
<i>You-- you need to leave</i>
<i>the house, you and Dad!</i>

52:54.438 --> 52:58.908
Your motherfucking mother
said to open this door!

52:58.910 --> 53:00.276
And, motherfuckers,

53:00.278 --> 53:04.380
you're going to open
this motherfucking door!

53:10.420 --> 53:12.888
[CRYING]

53:14.457 --> 53:15.858
Carly.

53:16.226 --> 53:17.893
Not so helpful.

53:17.895 --> 53:20.663
Joshie. [SOBBING]

53:21.298 --> 53:23.666
All right.
Let's try it this way.

53:23.668 --> 53:25.534
Where are you going?

53:45.288 --> 53:47.656
BRENT: That's not gonna cut
through this door.

53:47.658 --> 53:49.558
KENDALL: The hell it won't.

53:49.593 --> 53:50.993
It's a Sawzall.

53:50.995 --> 53:53.462
That means it saws all.

53:53.464 --> 53:56.765
Ah, well, you know,
educate me.

53:57.701 --> 53:59.602
[SAW WHIRRING]

54:00.637 --> 54:02.905
-[GRINDING]
-[GASPING]

54:07.410 --> 54:08.611
Fuck this.

54:08.613 --> 54:10.980
I'm tired of messing around
with this shit.

54:10.982 --> 54:12.815
You want to get things done?

54:13.617 --> 54:14.383
Huh?

54:14.385 --> 54:16.652
I'll get things done.

54:21.858 --> 54:24.260
Mom! Please don't!

54:24.828 --> 54:25.894
Please.

54:25.896 --> 54:28.897
[SCREAMING]

54:29.532 --> 54:30.699
[YELLS] What the fuck?

54:30.701 --> 54:34.003
-[GUNSHOTS]
-[KENDALL SCREAMING]

54:34.971 --> 54:37.473
[SCREAMS]

54:38.875 --> 54:41.810
[CONTINUES SCREAMING]

54:43.713 --> 54:45.748
[PANTING]

54:47.484 --> 54:49.585
[SCREAMS]

54:49.619 --> 54:51.420
Aw, shit!

54:51.422 --> 54:54.323
Got a fucking explanation
for this?

54:54.325 --> 54:54.990
You really went all in

54:54.992 --> 54:56.992
on the midlife crisis thing,
didn't you?

54:56.994 --> 54:58.394
A fucking handgun?
Really?

54:58.396 --> 55:01.363
Well, I mean, some psycho
could break into the house.

55:01.365 --> 55:02.731
How am I supposed to defend us?

55:02.733 --> 55:06.035
You do realize
that one in five children

55:06.037 --> 55:09.571
and adolescents injured
involve firearms!

55:09.573 --> 55:11.373
It was in a locked case.

55:11.375 --> 55:13.509
What was the combination?

55:14.711 --> 55:16.445
Josh's birthday.

55:23.920 --> 55:25.921
Who wants to die today?

55:27.324 --> 55:29.858
Speak! Speak!

55:30.026 --> 55:31.493
Come on.

55:33.496 --> 55:34.697
What a jerk you are.

55:34.699 --> 55:36.799
[IMITATES GUNSHOTS]

55:38.568 --> 55:39.835
Damn it!

55:39.903 --> 55:41.470
[SIGHS]

55:41.472 --> 55:42.604
Forget it.

55:42.606 --> 55:44.073
I have an idea.

55:44.908 --> 55:45.841
[SIGHS]

55:45.843 --> 55:47.776
Want to get me something
for this?

55:47.778 --> 55:49.912
Oh, you bet I will.

55:51.414 --> 55:54.516
KENDALL: Okay,
just get some alcohol.

55:54.518 --> 55:56.685
BRENT: Alcohol? Okay.

55:56.687 --> 55:57.953
Just alcohol. Okay.

55:57.955 --> 56:00.456
Maybe I should try
to take the bullet out first.

56:00.458 --> 56:03.125
Are you fucking kidding me?
No! No. Leave it.

56:03.127 --> 56:04.827
I just don't want it
to get infected.

56:04.829 --> 56:06.028
-Just leave it.
-Okay.

56:06.030 --> 56:08.630
You ready?
One, two, three, go.

56:08.632 --> 56:14.403
[SCREAMING]

56:14.405 --> 56:16.038
What-- what was that?

56:16.106 --> 56:16.805
It sounded like Mom.

56:16.807 --> 56:19.975
-[KENDALL GROANING]
-BRENT: All right. okay, okay.

56:19.977 --> 56:21.944
Opening. Don't hurt your teeth.

56:21.946 --> 56:23.011
-[GROANS]
-Okay, okay.

56:23.013 --> 56:25.914
Okay. Okay. Okay. Ow! Fuck!

56:25.916 --> 56:27.750
[BOTH SPIT]

56:27.752 --> 56:28.450
BRENT: All right.

56:28.452 --> 56:32.054
All right, okay. Here we go.
All right. And...

56:32.722 --> 56:33.922
one,

56:34.424 --> 56:35.691
two...

56:36.092 --> 56:37.493
three...

56:37.495 --> 56:38.560
five, six.

56:38.562 --> 56:40.963
Do you think Dad's hurting her?

56:41.698 --> 56:43.132
I don't know.

56:44.100 --> 56:46.402
I don't think so. I think...

56:48.004 --> 56:50.539
I think
they only want to hurt us.

56:53.042 --> 56:54.176
Don't worry.

56:54.178 --> 56:55.411
Everything's gonna be okay,

56:55.413 --> 56:57.913
'cause whatever's happening
out there...

56:58.181 --> 56:59.848
it's gonna pass.

57:00.617 --> 57:02.050
But until then...

57:02.419 --> 57:03.852
we're safe here, okay?

57:03.854 --> 57:05.554
No one can get in.

57:05.889 --> 57:07.556
Are you sure?

57:09.058 --> 57:10.626
[THUMPING]

57:12.729 --> 57:16.165
<i>♪ We're urban savages</i>
<i>No one can manage us ♪</i>

57:16.167 --> 57:19.001
♪ We're gonna hit the street

57:19.003 --> 57:22.638
<i>♪ We're urban savages</i>
<i>No one can manage us ♪</i>

57:22.640 --> 57:24.440
♪ We gotta rock the street ♪

57:24.442 --> 57:27.810
♪ Locked inside your city like
I'm locked inside your cage ♪

57:27.812 --> 57:30.979
<i>♪ Capitalist corruption</i>
<i>Is oozing off my brain ♪</i>

57:30.981 --> 57:34.550
♪ Put locks on your cities
Put locks on your stores ♪

57:34.552 --> 57:38.720
♪ Gonna burn your city down
<i>Right on the floor ♪</i>

57:43.593 --> 57:47.763
Kendall, this is a really
great idea, honey.

57:53.102 --> 57:54.803
[FLIES BUZZING]

57:54.805 --> 57:56.472
♪ Corruption turning into rage

57:56.474 --> 58:00.776
♪ <i>Put locks on your cities</i>
<i>And locks on your floor</i> ♪

58:00.778 --> 58:03.078
[FLIES BUZZING]

58:21.764 --> 58:26.134
♪ Trapped inside a system
Like a bird locked in a cage ♪

58:26.903 --> 58:28.871
KENDALL: <i>Okay! Let her rip!</i>

58:28.873 --> 58:30.506
BRENT: Gas on!

58:31.708 --> 58:32.040
Love you!

58:32.042 --> 58:36.044
♪ <i>Gonna burn your city down</i>
<i>Onto the floor</i> ♪

58:37.981 --> 58:39.515
<i>♪ Escape!</i>

58:40.116 --> 58:42.017
[GAS HISSING]

58:42.252 --> 58:43.986
Wait here, okay?

58:44.921 --> 58:45.621
What?

58:45.623 --> 58:47.723
-CARLY: Just wait here.
-Okay.

58:51.094 --> 58:54.730
[GASPING]

59:01.070 --> 59:02.704
[TAPE RIPPING]

59:05.275 --> 59:07.142
What the fuck?

59:28.331 --> 59:30.098
[GASPING]

59:32.101 --> 59:34.970
[GAS HISSING]

59:45.882 --> 59:48.183
I found Lisa outside...

59:48.185 --> 59:52.354
by the bins. That explains
the mess in the kitchen.

59:52.589 --> 59:53.822
Ah.

59:54.223 --> 59:56.224
I was wondering about that.

59:56.926 --> 59:57.726
Hmm.

59:57.728 --> 59:59.962
How long do you think
it'll take?

01:00:00.029 --> 01:00:01.196
I don't know.

01:00:01.198 --> 01:00:03.131
It's a big basement.

01:00:03.199 --> 01:00:05.667
We should hear them coughing.

01:00:05.735 --> 01:00:07.769
[CHUCKLES] Throwing up.

01:00:07.870 --> 01:00:09.137
[CHUCKLES]

01:00:09.139 --> 01:00:14.209
After that, we should be good
to cut the door down.

01:00:29.158 --> 01:00:32.194
[GAS HISSING]

01:00:39.769 --> 01:00:40.902
[COUGHING]

01:00:40.904 --> 01:00:43.305
Josh, are you okay?

01:00:43.339 --> 01:00:44.206
Hey...

01:00:44.208 --> 01:00:45.907
listen to me, okay?

01:00:45.909 --> 01:00:47.776
You gotta stay with me...

01:00:48.144 --> 01:00:48.910
okay?

01:00:48.912 --> 01:00:50.812
You have to stay with me.

01:00:51.381 --> 01:00:54.016
I don't know
why this is happening...

01:00:55.018 --> 01:00:55.951
and I don't know--

01:00:55.953 --> 01:00:58.086
[COUGHING] I don't know
what we could have done

01:00:58.088 --> 01:00:59.955
or not done to change it.

01:01:01.924 --> 01:01:03.825
But the fact is that...

01:01:04.360 --> 01:01:07.062
is that Mom and Dad
want to hurt us.

01:01:09.666 --> 01:01:11.967
They want to kill us.

01:01:12.802 --> 01:01:15.871
Okay, but we're not gonna
let that happen, all right?

01:01:16.272 --> 01:01:18.206
[GAS HISSING]

01:01:19.108 --> 01:01:21.176
We're gonna get out of here.

01:01:26.149 --> 01:01:27.949
[CLEARS THROAT]

01:01:28.284 --> 01:01:32.688
[COUGHING]

01:01:37.160 --> 01:01:40.128
[CONTINUES COUGHING]

01:02:22.305 --> 01:02:24.005
[COUGHING]

01:02:34.884 --> 01:02:36.384
You gonna hurt them?

01:02:36.386 --> 01:02:39.187
CARLY: Shh. Stay down. Go back.

01:02:40.022 --> 01:02:41.323
Your nose.

01:02:43.826 --> 01:02:46.027
[JOSH COUGHING]

01:03:16.926 --> 01:03:19.127
-[COUGHING]
-CARLY: Shh.

01:03:27.036 --> 01:03:28.270
Do it.

01:03:31.440 --> 01:03:32.874
Come on.

01:03:33.176 --> 01:03:34.910
[PANTING]

01:03:36.979 --> 01:03:38.446
[SAW WHIRRING]

01:03:38.448 --> 01:03:40.348
[COUGHS]

01:03:50.359 --> 01:03:51.960
[METAL CLANKING]

01:03:57.600 --> 01:03:59.434
-Come on.
-[JOSH COUGHS]

01:04:03.339 --> 01:04:04.940
[WHIRRING STOPS]

01:04:13.983 --> 01:04:15.350
Ah! Fuck!

01:04:21.290 --> 01:04:22.991
I don't see 'em.

01:04:31.100 --> 01:04:33.168
[PANTING]

01:04:36.539 --> 01:04:38.139
Stand back.

01:05:26.923 --> 01:05:29.958
[STATIC CRACKLES]

01:05:48.477 --> 01:05:49.945
[SIGHS]

01:05:57.153 --> 01:06:00.555
[WATER TRICKLING]

01:06:07.697 --> 01:06:09.164
[GRUNTS]

01:06:13.602 --> 01:06:15.737
[PANTING]

01:06:18.574 --> 01:06:20.108
[GASPS]

01:06:23.612 --> 01:06:25.213
Stay. Stay.

01:06:25.348 --> 01:06:28.183
Damn it, Carly! Get back here!

01:06:30.753 --> 01:06:33.088
[PANTING]

01:06:33.756 --> 01:06:35.323
[DOOR BANGS]

01:06:38.327 --> 01:06:40.762
CARLY: <i>Mom, no! Stop!</i>

01:06:41.530 --> 01:06:43.531
Stop! Mom!

01:06:43.533 --> 01:06:46.067
[PIANO PLAYING]

01:06:53.509 --> 01:06:55.076
KENDALL: Hey.

01:06:55.244 --> 01:06:55.710
Mommy...

01:06:55.712 --> 01:06:58.646
I'm sorry. I didn't mean to.

01:06:58.681 --> 01:07:01.383
Oh, no, no. No, honey.

01:07:01.617 --> 01:07:02.550
Honey, it's okay.

01:07:02.552 --> 01:07:05.487
You don't ever have to be afraid
of me.

01:07:06.756 --> 01:07:09.524
Oh, look how beautiful you are.

01:07:10.192 --> 01:07:12.193
You did a good job.

01:07:13.029 --> 01:07:14.295
Here.

01:07:16.298 --> 01:07:17.465
Just a kiss of it.

01:07:17.467 --> 01:07:20.035
There's your angel cheeks.

01:07:20.569 --> 01:07:22.604
Thank you for making me pretty,
Mommy.

01:07:22.606 --> 01:07:25.373
Oh, honey, you were born
that way.

01:07:26.742 --> 01:07:31.179
There is nothing I want more
in this world than to see you...

01:07:31.181 --> 01:07:32.547
[SCREAMS]

01:07:33.382 --> 01:07:34.616
Honey.

01:07:34.817 --> 01:07:36.584
CARLY: Mom. No!

01:07:36.719 --> 01:07:39.187
[SCREAMING]

01:07:39.189 --> 01:07:42.390
-[BITES]
-[SCREAMS]

01:07:48.064 --> 01:07:49.631
Mrs. Ryan, no!

01:07:52.435 --> 01:07:54.836
[GRUNTING]

01:07:55.137 --> 01:07:57.205
-KENDALL: Carly.
-CARLY: No!

01:07:57.207 --> 01:08:00.108
-Mom! No! No!
-[SNARLS]

01:08:00.276 --> 01:08:02.377
-Let go of me!
-CARLY: No!

01:08:02.478 --> 01:08:04.279
No. No, no, no.

01:08:04.281 --> 01:08:06.147
Baby, baby,
Carly, it's okay.

01:08:06.149 --> 01:08:08.450
Shh. Shh. It's okay.

01:08:08.751 --> 01:08:10.318
[GROANS]

01:08:13.389 --> 01:08:15.590
-Mom!
-KENDALL: It's okay, Carly.

01:08:15.758 --> 01:08:17.792
[GRUNTS]

01:08:19.095 --> 01:08:21.563
-[POUNDING]
-[GRUNTING]

01:08:23.666 --> 01:08:25.100
No!

01:08:28.203 --> 01:08:29.703
Holy shit!

01:08:29.772 --> 01:08:31.706
Mom, stop!

01:08:31.707 --> 01:08:33.475
[GASPING]

01:08:36.479 --> 01:08:38.479
[CARLY PANTING]

01:08:42.417 --> 01:08:43.885
[COUGHS]

01:08:46.589 --> 01:08:48.823
It's usually not this bad.

01:08:49.258 --> 01:08:50.625
[CHUCKLES]

01:08:52.528 --> 01:08:54.662
[LAUGHING]

01:09:00.603 --> 01:09:02.403
I used to think
my parents getting divorced

01:09:02.404 --> 01:09:04.305
was the hugest tragedy
of my life,

01:09:04.307 --> 01:09:08.542
but ironically, that shit
doubled my chance of survival.

01:09:08.545 --> 01:09:10.345
[BOTH LAUGHING]

01:09:16.484 --> 01:09:17.852
Where's Mom?

01:09:19.587 --> 01:09:20.889
-What?
-[SCREAMS]

01:09:20.890 --> 01:09:23.825
JOSH: Mom, stop it!
You're gonna hurt them!

01:09:23.827 --> 01:09:25.326
Mom!

01:09:26.729 --> 01:09:27.795
No!

01:09:27.796 --> 01:09:29.163
[CARLY GASPING]

01:09:29.166 --> 01:09:32.200
JOSH: No! Mom, stop!

01:09:33.301 --> 01:09:34.669
CARLY: No!

01:09:36.337 --> 01:09:37.906
[CARLY SCREAMS]

01:09:38.640 --> 01:09:41.309
CARLY: Damon? [PANTING]

01:09:45.314 --> 01:09:47.415
[GASPING]

01:09:48.917 --> 01:09:50.685
Mom, please, no!

01:09:57.226 --> 01:09:58.860
[GASPING]

01:09:58.894 --> 01:10:00.695
[WHIMPERS] Come on.

01:10:00.697 --> 01:10:02.297
Josh, come on.

01:10:05.267 --> 01:10:07.969
-[SAW WHIRRING]
-CARLY: [SCREAMS] Stop!

01:10:11.674 --> 01:10:14.742
[PANTING]

01:10:16.645 --> 01:10:17.979
Sawzall.

01:10:19.481 --> 01:10:20.848
Means it...

01:10:21.917 --> 01:10:23.351
saws...

01:10:23.686 --> 01:10:24.619
all.

01:10:24.621 --> 01:10:26.588
[SAW WHIRRING]

01:10:26.789 --> 01:10:28.957
CARLY: Daddy, please, no.

01:10:29.325 --> 01:10:31.326
[SOBBING]

01:10:32.494 --> 01:10:35.863
I'm sorry I said
that you have no life, okay?

01:10:35.865 --> 01:10:37.532
I'm sorry
that we don't talk anymore.

01:10:37.534 --> 01:10:39.300
I'm sorry
that we're not best friends--

01:10:39.302 --> 01:10:41.769
-Shh!
-Mom, we're a family.

01:10:41.771 --> 01:10:42.570
We love each other.

01:10:42.572 --> 01:10:43.838
When they can't stand
each other,

01:10:43.840 --> 01:10:46.774
-they give a shit.
-Whatever. Whatever.

01:10:47.509 --> 01:10:48.776
Saws...

01:10:49.445 --> 01:10:50.645
all.

01:10:52.581 --> 01:10:53.381
[JOSH WHIMPERS]

01:10:53.383 --> 01:10:55.984
CARLY: Close your eyes, bro.
Close your eyes.

01:11:00.723 --> 01:11:01.656
[SCREAMS]

01:11:01.658 --> 01:11:03.424
-[SCREAMING]
-No! Stop!

01:11:03.426 --> 01:11:05.026
[DOORBELL RINGS]

01:11:07.930 --> 01:11:08.930
Shit.

01:11:08.932 --> 01:11:11.399
I forgot. Your parents.

01:11:11.734 --> 01:11:13.468
That was tonight?

01:11:13.769 --> 01:11:15.837
-[DOORBELL RINGS]
-[SOBBING]

01:11:15.938 --> 01:11:17.572
God damn it.

01:11:17.706 --> 01:11:19.974
[KIDS PANTING]

01:11:21.710 --> 01:11:22.810
Just a sec.

01:11:22.812 --> 01:11:23.678
[DOORBELL CONTINUES RINGING]

01:11:23.680 --> 01:11:28.283
BRENT: <i>All right, all right.</i>
<i>Hold your horses. Jesus!</i>

01:11:28.617 --> 01:11:30.685
Mom, Dad, listen.

01:11:30.687 --> 01:11:31.953
[SCREAMS]

01:11:31.955 --> 01:11:33.421
[GRUNTS]

01:11:34.290 --> 01:11:35.556
[GROANS]

01:11:37.393 --> 01:11:38.893
[CLATTERING]

01:11:39.561 --> 01:11:41.696
Dad! [SCREAMS]

01:11:43.732 --> 01:11:44.966
[GROANS]

01:11:47.569 --> 01:11:49.704
Oh! Holy shit!

01:11:49.772 --> 01:11:52.006
Dad! You killed me!

01:11:52.008 --> 01:11:53.975
You fucking killed me!

01:11:53.977 --> 01:11:55.643
Nah, bullshit.

